cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper is about the design and integration of perception, state estimation, and system components for an autonomous racecar. This falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO) and involves computer vision (cs.CV) for LiDAR-based perception, control systems (cs.SY) for state estimation and control, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for decision-making, and machine learning (cs.LG) for particle filter-based SLAM.
